        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">A </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Slide-Joint</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> constrains </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Sketch-Element-Line" styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Lines</link><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">* from two separate </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">parts</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> to be collinear. (*</text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Lines</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> or </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">CAD-Lines</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">). </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">The </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Symbols" styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">symbol</link><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> for the </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Slide-Joint</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> is </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><image src="Red-14-1b.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">a narrow rectangle</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> a wide rectangle </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><image src="Red-14-3.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">an arrowhead indicates the positive direction.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Each rectangle is along the full length of each Line that you select to add the Slide-Joint.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#ff6600;" /></para>
